{
  "stem": "11272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the only time, really, the entire time that I saw any emotion that-- that they might lose the war, and they should stop doing it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other than that, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's a-- That's-- that's something that neither Elie Wiesel or I or any one of us survivors have really been able to figure out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess the-- the main thing that was in my mind-- my commitment to Father, Mother that no matter what, I'm going to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also you had to be very strong to try and help your fellow man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because too many people were ready to give up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Many times, you woke up and person next to you was dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and somehow if-- if-- if they were having any breathing in them, any warmth, you kept on shaking and making sure-- please, please, please, come on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Wake up!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Wake up!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Wake up!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we got very little sleep over there for many reasons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Number one, you know, we had no mattresses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had no straw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had these rough boards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we didn't have-- we couldn't lay flat, because we had only this much room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of all, you had to guard your bread, because if people thought that you were dead, they took your bread away from you or took your pants off of you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So you had stay up all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When I tell people now that if I'm lucky I get two, three hours sleep a night, they can't believe it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But that's true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I feel very fortunate if I can get that much sleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That camp has-- has taught me-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] suffering beyond any human understanding.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
